</p>
<a href="https://wa.me/5511983134656?text=Olá,%20gostaria%20de%20saber%20sobre%20acupuntura%20para%20dores%20nas%20costas." class="text-primary font-bold hover:text-secondary flex items-center gap-2 text-lg">
Voltar a Me Mover <span class="text-xl">&rarr;</span>
</a>
</div>

<div id="enxaqueca" class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100 hover:border-primary/50 transition-colors">
